"{\"uid\": \"dailypost.ng-2024-02-23-super-falcons-ready-to-end-olympic-games-absence-nnadozie\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Published  on  By  Chiamaka Nnadozie says the Super Falcons will give their all to earn a berth at the 2024 Olympic Games, DAILY POST reports.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 142, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19, \"end\": 36, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chiamaka_Nnadozie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chiamaka Nnadozie\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chiamaka_Nnadozie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chiamaka_Nnadozie\"}, {\"begin\": 46, \"end\": 59, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Super Falcons\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 123, \"end\": 133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_Daily_Post\", \"score\": 0.9999999979179393, \"rank\": 2.0821064046104306e-09, \"text\": \"DAILY POST\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_Daily_Post\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_Daily_Post\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The nine-time African champions failed to qualify for the last three editions of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 144, \"to\": 238, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The West Africans last appeared at the sporting fiesta in Beijing 2008.\", \"from\": 240, \"to\": 311, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 298, \"end\": 310, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999968017262958, \"rank\": 3.0705208186428933e-06, \"text\": \"Beijing 2008\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Randy Waldrum's side will confront perennial rivals, Cameroon in the first leg of their third round tie at the Stade de la Reunification, Douala, on Friday (today).\", \"from\": 313, \"to\": 477, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 313, \"end\": 326, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Waldrum\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Randy Waldrum\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Waldrum\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Waldrum\"}, {\"begin\": 366, \"end\": 374, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameroon_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9997650378577316, \"rank\": 0.00022328594952276948, \"text\": \"Cameroon\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameroon_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameroon_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ahead of the highly anticipated encounter, Nnadozie claimed the Super Falcons can not afford to miss out on the ticket again.\", \"from\": 479, \"to\": 604, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 543, \"end\": 556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Super Falcons\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I know it's been long we qualified for the Olympics but this is a new phase and we have to focus on it,\\\" the Paris FC goalie told a press conference.\", \"from\": 606, \"to\": 756, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 716, \"end\": 724, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_FC\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.307966898394954e-20, \"text\": \"Paris FC\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_FC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_FC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The girls are ready, we know what it takes and we know everyone is expecting us to qualify.\", \"from\": 758, \"to\": 850, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are in good spirit and the coach is very confident in us and we hope to qualify this time.\\\"\", \"from\": 852, \"to\": 947, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Acknowledging Cameroon's formidable squad, she added, \\\"Cameroon is a very good side with exceptional players whom we respect, but tomorrow (today), we have to come out strong.\", \"from\": 949, \"to\": 1124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 963, \"end\": 971, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameroon_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9997650378577316, \"rank\": 0.00022328594952276948, \"text\": \"Cameroon\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameroon_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameroon_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1004, \"end\": 1012, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameroon_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9997650378577316, \"rank\": 0.00022328594952276948, \"text\": \"Cameroon\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameroon_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameroon_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are confident.\", \"from\": 1125, \"to\": 1142, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I believe in our team, and we are ready to play this game.\\\"\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1202, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Cameroon vs Nigeria: All you need to know about 2024 Olympic qualifier  EPL: Jim Ratcliffe to make three new signings for Man Utd  2026 WAFCON: 'It would not happen for other tourna